index.html
A display area to show elapsed time
Start, Pause, and Reset buttons

syle.css
Center the stopwatch
Make the timer large and readable
Style the buttons differently for easy identification

script.js
Formatting time correctly

Converts milliseconds to minutes, seconds, and milliseconds.
Ensures two-digit formatting using .padStart(2, '0').
Starting the stopwatch

Uses setInterval() to update the display every 10ms.
Calculates elapsed time using Date.now().
Pausing the stopwatch

Stops the interval using clearInterval().
Resetting the stopwatch

Resets elapsed time and clears the display.
